data.description: Prime location in Miami, TX!  Country living feel w/ no drive!  Located on 2 lots, this beautiful, spacious open floor plan home is ready for you. The owner has put a nice large new wooden porch on the front (updated pics to come) to enjoy the amazing views this property provides.  Brand new AC unit installed 8/23.  New water line w/ washer & dryer hook ups in the garage- solar panels w/ app to see the production and usage of the energy the panels are producing and the what the home is using- google nest.  4 bed - 2 bathrooms, open floor plan- spacious master bathroom w/ a dreamy master bathroom!!  Fenced in backyard, carport, RV hookup and more!
